About Cucumber Reports

Library generating different Cucumber reports

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Cucumber Runner The part of Cucumber Reports library which contains extended Cucumber-JVM runners and all relevant functionality.
Cucumber Reporting Maven Plugin Maven plugin responsible for extended reports generation.
Cucumber Report Generator The part of the Cucumber Reports library directly responsible for reports generation.
